ygData.messageBody:
Being a dark elf....the cities I can travel too aren't too many. I've
seen the troll city....not much there for me. I haven't been to Oggok but
i hear its a semi decent town. Qeynos I now hear is KOS. I have been
into Freeport and walked around a bit....just have to /con alot...bu the
guards won't attack me if i don't bother them. Are there any other cities
out there....that Dark Elves can go into that anyone knows of.

So far

Freeport
Neriak
Grobb
Oggok

anything else?

Korm
